2. Retrieve all movies in the Drama genre with rating higher than 8.5

SQL Query
SELECT title, genre, rating 
FROM Movies 
WHERE genre = 'Drama' AND rating > 8.5;

Result:


| title           | genre | rating |
| --------------- | ----- | ------ |
| Stranger Things | Drama | 8.7    |


