3. Find average rating of all movies released after 2015

QL Query

SELECT AVG(rating) AS average_rating 
FROM Movies 
WHERE release_year > 2015;

Result

average_rating
8.5

=============

4. List users who watched Stranger Things with completion percentage

SQL Query

SELECT U.name, W.completion_percentage 
FROM Users U 
JOIN WatchHistory W ON U.user_id = W.user_id
JOIN Movies M ON W.movie_id = M.movie_id 
WHERE M.title = 'Stranger Things';

Result

| name     | completion_percentage |
| -------- | --------------------- |
| John Doe | 100                   |


============

5. Find users who gave highest review rating

SQL Query

SELECT U.name 
FROM Users U 
JOIN Reviews R ON U.user_id = R.user_id 
WHERE R.rating = (SELECT MAX(rating) FROM Reviews);

Result

name
Jane Smith

=========

6. Calculate number of movies watched by each user

SQL Query

SELECT U.name, COUNT(W.watch_id) AS movies_watched 
FROM Users U 
JOIN WatchHistory W ON U.user_id = W.user_id 
GROUP BY U.user_id 
ORDER BY movies_watched DESC;

Result

| name          | movies_watched |
| ------------- | -------------- |
| John Doe      | 2              |
| Jane Smith    | 1              |
| Alice Johnson | 1              |
| Bob Brown     | 1              |


===========

7. List all movies watched by John Doe with genre, rating and completion percentage

SQL Query

SELECT M.title, M.genre, M.rating, W.completion_percentage 
FROM Movies M
JOIN WatchHistory W ON M.movie_id = W.movie_id
JOIN Users U ON W.user_id = U.user_id
WHERE U.name = 'John Doe';

Result

| title           | genre  | rating | completion_percentage |
| --------------- | ------ | ------ | --------------------- |
| Stranger Things | Drama  | 8.7    | 100                   |
| Black Mirror    | Sci-Fi | 8.8    | 90                    |


